<span id="freeTextContainer2869006684295186001">Insightful and earnestly written, the book is packed with interesting anecdotes and philosophy with actual substance. It serves as an inspiration that a healthy, thriving work culture is possible and can constantly be improved. His never ending determination to create good work and foster a good company is admirable and should be replicated to any company, but especially those in the creative field.</span>

